snippet: On Saturday, McKayla Maroney continued U.S. dominance in the vault at the world gymnastics championships as an American won the gold medal for the third consecutive year.
lead_paragraph: On Saturday, McKayla Maroney continued U.S. dominance in the vault at the world gymnastics championships as an American won the gold medal for the third consecutive year.

headline.main: Another U.S. Gymnast Wins Gold Medal in Vault
